This repo contains dvipdf and supporting files.

-----------------------------

Put *.pfb files from the following archives to this directory:

https://www.ams.org/arc/tex/amsfonts.zip
https://mirrors.ctan.org/fonts/ps-type1/cm-super.zip

--------------------------------------------------------------------

To correctly copy/search quoteleft, minus and quoteright:

1)
sed -i '/#0060/s/SD130000/quoteleft/' Resource/Decoding/Unicode
sed -i '/#2018/s/quoteleft/SD130000/' Resource/Decoding/Unicode
sed -i '/#002D/s/SP100000/minus/' Resource/Decoding/Unicode
sed -i '/#2212/s/minus/SP100000/' Resource/Decoding/Unicode
sed -i '/#0027/s/SP050000/quoteright/' Resource/Decoding/Unicode
sed -i '/#2019/s/quoteright/SP050000/' Resource/Decoding/Unicode

2)
1. dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot -b -us -uc
2. grep -srn pdf_simple_font_needs_ToUnicode .
3. objdump -S <libgs that will be found by grep> >/tmp/1
4. In the end of function pdf_simple_font_needs_ToUnicode change 'return false' to 'return true'
5. dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot -b -us -uc
6. objdump -S <libgs that will be found by grep> >/tmp/2
7. diff /tmp/1 /tmp/2

-    return false;
- 82c7f3d:	b8 00 00 00 00       	mov    $0x0,%eax
+    return true;
+ 82c7f3d:	b8 01 00 00 00       	mov    $0x1,%eax

xxd -p -c1 lib/modules/*/cdc-acm.ko >dump
patch dump <<'EOF'
@@ -5334,7 +5334,7 @@
 04
 82
 8c
-03
+00
 00
 06
 24
EOF
FILE=`ls lib/modules/*/cdc-acm.ko`
rm $FILE # xxd does not overwrite existing output file
xxd -r -p dump $FILE

(To see the effect of this, add -dCompressFonts=false to ps2pdf,
open pdf file via 'less' and search CMap.)
